Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:23.46,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(298,0)}We sigh whenever we're about to come to a standstill
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:29.71,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}While moving on this endless journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:37.43,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Everytime we lunge for it, it escapes and flies off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:44.85,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}But now, there's nothing to be afraid of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:52.78,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}The powerful ties that bind our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:58.24,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Will never come loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:07.96,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9}After a lifetime of searching, we finally arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:13.76,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Here, where the period lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:23.06,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}Let's change all our sorrow and rage to power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:27.98,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,298}Destiny is right within our reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:23.46,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(298,0)}終わりなき旅の途中　立ち止まりそうな時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:29.71,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}深いため息こぼす　僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:37.43,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}掴みかけてはまた離れていった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:44.85,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}でも今はもう何も恐れることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:52.78,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}心を繋ぐ強い絆は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:58.24,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}けして解けはしないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:07.96,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9}探し続けて辿り着いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:13.76,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}この場所で {\fsp8}Perio{\fsp3.2}d に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:23.06,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}悲しみ怒り 力に変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:27.98,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,298}運命はすぐそばに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:23.46,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(298,0)}Owarinaki tabi no tochuu tachidomarisouna toki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:29.71,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Fukai tameiki kobosu bokura wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:37.43,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Tsukamikaketewa mata hanareteitta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:44.85,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Demo ima wa mou nanimo osoreru koto wa nai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:52.78,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}Kokoro wo tsunagu tsuyoi kizuna wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:58.24,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Keshite hodoke wa shinai sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:07.96,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9}Sagashitsuzukete tadoritsuita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:13.76,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Kono basho de piriodo ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:23.06,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}Kanashimi ikari chikara ni kaete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:27.98,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,298}Unmei wa sugu soba ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:03.30,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}The promise we never made
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.09,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:08.93,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}tries to snatch our future away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.55,0:22:14.52,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that we can't rejoice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:15.52,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}straight from the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:20.48,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}when we obtain something we've always been after?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:26.19,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,498}The overflowing tears aren't from feebleness or remorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.99,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,258)}They're fragments born from agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:36.04,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Of all the moments and destinies,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:44.80,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I realized there's one absolute certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:47.34,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if things get tough and I'm at my limit
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:51.34,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:56.22,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:23:04.07,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I can feel the warmth of your right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:07.74,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}where it's tightly joined with my left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:03.30,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}交わしたはずのない約束が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.09,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}今日も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:08.93,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}僕らの未来を奪おうとする
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.55,0:22:14.52,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,欲しがっていたものを手にしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:15.52,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}素直に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:20.48,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}うまく笑えないのはなぜだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:26.19,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,498}あふれる涙は　弱さや後悔じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.99,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,258)}イタミが生んだカケラで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:36.04,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}どんな瞬間だって運命だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:44.80,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}ひとつだけ確かなものがあると知った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:47.34,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,限界だって困難だって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:51.34,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,あきらめたくないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:56.22,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,このまま離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:23:04.07,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}かたく握りしめた　君の右手のぬくもり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:07.74,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}ここにあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:03.30,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Kawashita hazu no nai yakasoku ga
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:04.09,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Kyou mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.09,0:22:08.93,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}Bokura no mirai wo ubaou to suru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.55,0:22:14.52,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshigatteita mono wo te ni shitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:15.52,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Sunao ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:20.48,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}Umaku waraenai nowa nazedarou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:26.19,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,498}Afureru namida wo yowasa ya koukai ja nai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.86,0:22:30.99,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,258)}Itami ga unda kakera de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:36.04,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Donna shunkan datte unmei datte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:44.80,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Hitotsu dake tashika na mono ga aru to shitta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:47.34,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Genkai datte konnan datte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:51.34,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Akirametakunaiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.34,0:22:56.22,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Konomama hanasanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.22,0:23:04.07,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Kataku nigirishimeta kimi no migite no nukumori
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:07.74,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}Koko ni arukara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.42,0:01:36.43,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:37.74,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.01,0:01:42.42,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,So... I heard from Pinako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.88,0:01:44.75,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,About what happened to your body and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:55.44,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:59.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoh, do you think you could lend us a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:00.99,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:02.91,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Let's catch up on things later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:03.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:16.40,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That radio you guys fixed for me back then has been working great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.95,0:02:19.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's no static coming from it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:27.75,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. All of this happened because we messed with Cornello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:29.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.43,0:02:33.90,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The city came to its senses because you two exposed his crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:36.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there was a riot, but look at it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:43.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't those beautiful sounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:46.47,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They're rebuilding the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:49.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving no resentment behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:54.06,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go help out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.06,0:02:55.96,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Please look after Winry for me, Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:01.26,Default,Jer,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll see what we can help out with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:02.43,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Yoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:03.41,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:04.83,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,What about food?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:08.46,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,It'll taste better if you eat {\i1}after{\i0\fscx40} {\r} you work!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:09.80,Default,Zam,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.80,0:03:11.18,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:12.71,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.45,0:03:16.81,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That was your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.25,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that must have been awfully rude of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:22.18,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been a while since you've seen him.\NCan you really just leave him hanging?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:26.18,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I left the house many years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:29.18,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he trusts me as a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:31.75,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Not really sure what to talk about with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:32.56,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:37.92,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:40.19,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:44.77,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take that for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:50.66,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.70,0:04:00.51,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,How's the bath, Winry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.55,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:06.55,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even remember the last time I soaked in the tub...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.88,0:04:08.60,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave your change of clothes right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:10.31,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.65,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Rose's so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:19.12,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,I find you really admirable, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:22.89,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,You're so young, but you've already set yourself up in the automail business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:24.95,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make Ed's leg too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.24,0:04:26.41,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:28.95,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,We're old friends, so it was the least I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.72,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:33.93,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the one who gave Ed a leg so he could stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:37.61,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,Then in turn, he gave me the strength to stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:40.27,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,So in a way, you saved me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:46.43,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,I was told my late boyfriend could be revived.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:51.97,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing that and believing in their miracles, I gave myself up to Leto.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:58.44,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,That was just around the time when Ed and Al came here and exposed the priest's lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:04.08,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,What I've been clinging on to just disappeared like that, so I was feeling pretty hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.71,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,And that was when Ed scolded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:13.08,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to get up and keep on going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:17.52,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry! He's always like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:20.34,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't he be nicer about things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.38,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,It {\i1}was{\i0\fscx20} {\r} nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:25.31,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,That was Ed's kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.72,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,You're aware of that too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:34.36,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to him, we came to our senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:36.31,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in this city, including myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:44.65,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,We're all trying to get back on our feet without relying on miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.17,Default,Rose,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to Ed and Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:51.88,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Ed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:06:01.06,Default,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I followed those soldiers, but I ended up in some crazy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.52,0:06:03.46,Default,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Greed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:33.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What is and is not ethical changes with time and also depends on whom you ask.{episode 43}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:35.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That is not the reason.{episode 43}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.29,0:06:40.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It is to prevent an individual from creating a powerful army of their own, Major General.{episode 43}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:45.25,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,They're not actually human...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.71,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,They're dolls, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:47.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:53.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We will create soldiers by inserting souls into these humanoids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:57.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They will be the ultimate soldiers that obey our every command.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:07:00.00,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, an immortal army.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:03.15,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind if I ask something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:04.73,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:10.24,Default,Oli,0000,0000,0000,,Where would you obtain the souls to attach to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:16.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,From the people of the countries we've crushed, and have yet to crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:22.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The battlefield will become a hunting ground where we can obtain thousands of souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Central is scary!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.87,0:07:29.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's unbelievably cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:32.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Mr. Greed would be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:40.98,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,An underground tunnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:42.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:44.98,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to check whether there's one under this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.13,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,If there is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No, there has to be! Then-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:48.89,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Hold that thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:50.65,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take this somewhere private.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:58.16,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,So you came to Lior to prevent the activation of the Nationwide Transmutation Circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:07:59.07,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:01.71,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Then I found {\i1}you{\i0\fscx30} {\r} here! What a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.71,0:08:04.17,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me feel lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:08.50,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We met a man who looks just like you underneath Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I seriously doubt that there's no link between you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.93,0:08:14.45,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you knew who he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:17.01,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure this is a good idea, Alphonse?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:22.06,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,What if I was on their side?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:28.26,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you consider the possibility that everything you just said could make it to the enemy's ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:41.17,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy that you trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:42.45,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.56,0:08:44.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:49.96,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,So he's trusting a failure like me as a real father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:52.74,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:56.86,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's {\i1}my{\i0\fscx30} {\r} turn to trust my sons and to tell them everything I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:00.47,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:03.97,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I want Edward to hear it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:07.44,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:10.71,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,...has gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:22.33,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help the next customer, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:31.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to make a withdrawal from State Alchemist Edward Elric's research account.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:33.37,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Would that be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:34.99,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm here on his behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:37.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I have a power of attorney and also his signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:40.93,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.07,0:09:47.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This is the northern branch of Banks Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.52,0:09:52.44,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A withdrawal has just been made from\NState Alchemist Mr. Edward Elric's account.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:55.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The man claimed to be here on his behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:58.45,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He was a very large man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.75,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:07.20,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. This should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:10.58,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus, what a rip-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.78,0:10:12.67,Default,Doc2,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.67,0:10:15.21,Default,Doc2,0000,0000,0000,,With the hush money included, this is just the right amount.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:20.12,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we appreciate your not probing into our matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:20.76,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Darius!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:26.81,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,They caught up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:31.13,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:32.69,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:34.62,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.62,0:10:36.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:38.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is he your only patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:40.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone staying in the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:42.33,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,Just one in the back-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:52.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the only one staying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:54.45,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:57.45,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who went to the bank, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:00.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:05.52,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:06.81,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Are you from this clinic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:09.40,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Both hands in the air, slowly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:14.44,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen anyone going in and out of this clinic recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:18.44,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,His characteristics are...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:19.40,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:21.28,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Both hands in the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:24.77,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Red coat, blonde hair in a braid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:26.28,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,...and very short.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:30.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:32.21,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Harris!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:33.80,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Get yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.80,0:11:35.29,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Who did this to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.09,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Harri-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:46.33,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Cohen! Harris!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.47,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:05.95,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't bother to save any for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.55,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:10.75,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't fully recovered yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:13.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like a patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.02,0:12:18.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at full throttle and ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.80,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.80,0:12:30.52,Default,Doc,0000,0000,0000,,No need to thank me. Just go already!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:33.35,Default,Doc2,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to trouble us any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:40.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So they're looking for a blonde guy in a red coat who has his hair in a braid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:43.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll stay like this for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:46.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Put down your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:48.24,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,There's more of them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:51.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hands above your head! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:51.95,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.58,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from those two! They're dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:59.34,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're{\i0\fscx30} {\r} the one that's going to freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.71,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,You want to see this kid's head get blown off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.64,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to secure a vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.35,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:24.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They're after us, Donkey Kong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.20,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They're catching up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:29.37,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,They're from the northern army!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.99,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,I can't outrun them in the snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.37,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:39.63,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,How's it looking like in the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:42.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Bad! They're catching up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.21,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:44.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Take that right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.96,0:13:45.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Get on that street!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:46.59,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:47.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:48.76,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.35,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get you at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:53.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you get past the corner, make a u-turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.35,0:13:56.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:00.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.95,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.57,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I think they made that turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:19.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That worked out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:22.46,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... transmute it back to something simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:23.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This looks badass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.01,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:28.55,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:29.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a problem with my design?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:33.68,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Too many to list!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:41.44,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,We have nowhere to go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:42.65,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:49.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I wasted so much time because I let my guard down against Kimblee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:54.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Al was able to meet up with Winry and them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:57.04,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Fullmetal! You listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.96,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:02.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:05.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'd just like some information right now,\Nwhatever that may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We need to meet up with Al and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.55,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,So where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:11.34,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Where do we go to meet up with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:16.81,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Where would Al go...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Think... Think...!{no, not a jimmy neutron reference ~koki}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:28.19,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:33.20,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Well... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:36.33,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You were a slave, and now you're a philosopher's stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.91,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:42.42,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it's pretty unbelievable after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.21,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:50.42,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You'd have to be crazy to believe a story like that out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:57.06,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I guess I'm crazy then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:00.48,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You accept things pretty quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:02.52,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I'm pretty nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:07.82,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But... I guess it's easier to believe because my body is also like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:16.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... how does it feel to be immortal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:17.91,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,"How does it feel"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:21.29,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's convenient in many ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:26.50,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,But it's sad that I have to see my loved ones go before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.17,0:16:29.17,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:39.60,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Dad, you're a philosopher's stone,\Nwhich means your body isn't exactly normal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.47,0:16:42.56,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Then are Brother and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:45.44,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Are you asking whether you two are normal humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.60,0:16:47.44,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:49.69,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:53.53,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,My soul is fused with the philosopher's stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:57.87,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,but the actual core that holds me together is myself, a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:02.45,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,But the one at Central...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:06.50,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,He's only wearing a shell that resembles me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.87,0:17:08.38,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,A shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:09.67,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:14.17,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,So if you break the shell, you should be able to defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:15.84,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,"Defeat"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:17.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:24.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they trying to recreate the tragedy at Xerxes by using this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:27.98,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't stop them soon, there'll be a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:30.44,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:32.36,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,You've figured out this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:35.49,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,And this one must be the reverse transmutation circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:39.32,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The quick way would be to destroy the underground tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:40.78,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That's why-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:42.12,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:47.50,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,A powerful homunculus by the name of Pride lurks in the tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:51.00,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But if we don't hurry, their transmutation circle will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:54.71,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,It may already be complete, or has been for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Then all the more reason to...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.51,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,"The Day" hasn't come yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:01.80,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,"The Day"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.31,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.89,0:18:07.27,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be focused on what's at your feet. Look above you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:10.81,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, you'll be able to see new things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:11.40,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Above...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:13.48,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:16.40,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Sun God Leto?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:20.32,Default,Hohen,0000,0000,0000,,He's waiting for "The Day".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:28.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What did {\i1}I{\i0\fscx30} {\r} do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:41.43,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:43.60,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Lively people like you make me smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.68,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea how boring it is to guard this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:49.56,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real pleasure having someone like you visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:54.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Ultimate Shield...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:57.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Along with that tone and the way you laugh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:19:00.53,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you for mimicking Mr. Greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.20,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I'm Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.24,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Surprised you knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:07.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The greedy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:08.54,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.62,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,This entire world belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:14.59,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I want money, women, status, fame...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.59,0:19:16.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,"And everything else in this world!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:19.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:20.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,But it has to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.59,0:19:22.34,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:25.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:31.64,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:33.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.27,0:19:35.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Bido from Dublith!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.15,0:19:37.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You forgot your friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:39.32,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Dublith!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.32,0:19:42.32,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it all makes sense now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:43.45,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.07,0:19:46.41,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:48.33,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably talking about the previous Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.33,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:53.37,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:55.29,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. G...reed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:58.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're... friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.80,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Getting rid of intruders is my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.22,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:09.81,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:24.49,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:28.49,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten pretty low, Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:33.50,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell did you kill your own friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.66,0:20:36.38,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't... my friend...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.46,0:20:42.47,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about these memories?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:45.89,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to say that Bido guy was spitting out lies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:49.56,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,They're memories of the previous Greed, not mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.81,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you wracked with pain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:56.19,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Get your shit together, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:21:00.94,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,If you start to lose it, my soul will steal back my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:06.16,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,The previous Greed's soul had its memories wiped and purified.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:09.03,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I've forgotten all of my past!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:12.25,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,My ass you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:16.12,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Friends are connected by heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:21.09,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just rinse off something that's stained on your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:23.46,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:25.76,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Your very being is crying out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:31.35,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You've cut down a family member that was connected to you by soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:33.14,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:35.73,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to be greedy enough to want to keep {\i1}everything{\i0\fscx30} {\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:37.73,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,You disgust me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.95,0:23:20.87,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,What about this book?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.75,0:23:24.71,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,I read it when I was about your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.29,0:23:28.21,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,It's a tale about an adventurer who travels around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:31.34,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.35,0:23:42.48,Default,Wife,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.83,0:24:00.96,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The battle has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:03.71,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,No one can hold back his anger anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.29,0:24:07.21,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of them will survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.46,0:24:11.88,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And what is the truth that is\Ngradually revealed after the duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.01,0:24:17.26,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.26,0:24:20.89,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 45, The Promised Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.60,0:24:25.81,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Those who share the same ambition, gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.81,0:24:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
